nodes.text: The appearance of Tetarick sea urchin was similar to that of Lu Nan when the latter wore a special armored vest with mutliple straps and metal shackles that held together a dozen rifles, six shotguns, and a modified DF-q91 sniper rifle the height of herself around 82 BBY. At the time, Lu, a large human member of the Knights of Silver Dawn's red apricot squad, was preparing to train with the latest member of the squad, Sean, at the training ground of the red apricot base on the Outer Rim Territories planet Wind.
